    "This nuanced difference between pre-trained and final models stands as a hallmark of the BERT framework.",
    "GPT2 [4]OpenAI introduced the Generative Pre-trained Transformer (GPT) model in their paper titled \"Improving Language Understanding by Generative Pre-Training. \"",
